lyrics:
5 contributorsinside out lyricsverse 1
here a little sympathy for you to waste on me

even if i wanted to

verse 2

you got me upside down
maybe i was holding on too tight

even if i wanted to

just turn your back away and leave

see yellowcard liveget tickets as low as 30you might also likebridge
the two of us we dream like one
the two of us the two of us
the two of us take breath like one
the two of us the two of us x2

but everyday im learning how to make it through this life im in
